A '''Vuin-li''' was a type of egg-laying ceremony of the [[Issori]] species. It was a bond between a noble family and a common family from another realm. Vuin-lis were heavily frowned upon as forbidden, and it was believed that they never happened.<ref name="X-Wing Isard's Revenge">''[[X-Wing: Isard's Revenge]]''</ref>

